                    <p class="lang-en">The wax is heated to the desired temperature and then applied evenly to the area to be treated. After cooling, the wax is quickly and precisely removed, pulling the hair along with its root from the skin. This process can, with regular application, cause the hair to grow back thinner and sparser.</p>
